This folder contains the four following files :
1 - The Gerber files for manufacturing the 4-layer PCB (Altium Designer CAM format);
2 - A partial Digikey BOM for the hand-soldering assembly step (not in the standard Digikey cart format);
3 - A JLCPCB-formatted BOM file to upload when placing a PCBA order;
4 - A JLCPCB-formatted Pick and Place file to upload when placing a PCBA order;
